<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="go-off">go off</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>离开：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't go off without saying good-bye.
不要不辞而别。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>突然响起；走火；爆炸：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I overslept this morning because my morning clock didn't go off.
今天早晨闹钟没有响，所以我睡过头了。</p><footer>2009 江西</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The gun went off by accident.
枪不小心走火了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>熄灭；中断供应</strong></h4>
<p>反 go on </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Suddenly the lights went off.
灯突然熄灭了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>While I was cooking supper, the electricity went off.
我正在做晚饭时停电了。</p></div></div>